title: MARVEL TALES (1964-1994 series) Original Stories SIEGEL, LAYTON
description:
Here's a torrent of 10 original stories from Marvel Tales (1964-1994 series). This contains:

1. Angel (Warren Worthington) by Jerry Siegel and George Tuska, from Marvel Tales #30
2. Hawkeye and the Two-Gun Kid, from Marvel Tales #100
3. Hercules by Bob Layton, from Marvel Tales #197
4. Spider-Man vs. The Thing, from Marvel Tales #198
5 and 6. Rocket Racer by Tony Isabella, from Marvel Tales #242 and #250
7. Trapster vs. Ghost Rider by Scott Lobdell, from Marvel Tales #255
8. Freaks by Dan Slott, from Marvel Tales #256
9. X-Men, from Marvel Tales #262
10. Woodgod by Scott Lobdell, from Marvel Tales #263

All credit goes to the scanner. Please seed and share.  --STF
